name: /rozriz glitch/
description: These are visual reflections on human preparation.  If everything is a simulation, what parts and patterns are we made of?  The explosion of the pixels of our form will not remove consciousness, everything is one with the cosmos - the higher consciousness.  I've been putting together this puzzle for several weeks, going back and creating new glitch resolutions, reshaping the space around the ideal creation - the human body.  My feelings are forever sealed in forms and rhythms.
